		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Ok here is what I did to complete this Quest.<BR>
<BR>
1) Give a lot of Orc Picks to Guard Valon and raise your Faction with<BR>
the militia. Once you have raised your faction enough Guard Valon asks<BR>
you to get 8 Dervish Cutthroat rings and put them in a puch which he gives<BR>
you. Place 8 Dervish Cutthroat rings in the pouch and hit combine. Then give<BR>
the pouch back to Guard Valon and he gives you a coin. Take the coin to West<BR>
Freeport to a guard in the Milita House names Captain Hazran. He will give you<BR>
a Reserve Milita Tunic with an AC of 9 and a +3 Dex.<BR>

